t calculations). For C, communication difficulty and egocentric attitude could affect crew coordination. For D, teamwork issues severe. For A, unknown reliability and unfriendly.\n\nThus C seems best overall despite communication issues. As agent_3, we may shift vote to C. We should also ask if any other agents have any positive teamwork info for D or reliability for A. But they already said no. Still we can ask again to confirm.\n\nWe need to produce public message: summarize evaluation, note missing info, ask targeted question, and state our vote (maybe Candidate C). Provide reasoning.\n\nNow produce final output."}
